divs: Sighting DetailsI seen a UFO last night June 24 2012 in New London WI. 10:25 pm to be exact. it flew real low over my house. It was huge. Had bright orange glowing lights it looked like a fireball in the sky. as I looked up I noticed way up in the sky two other UFO's flying around. Now these were super fast they were north then south back and forth.then the big one went up and vanished. And the two other ones went south and disappeared. So I sat outside looking to the sky to see if I could see anything else, when a jet flew over at 11:15 real low and following the same path as the UFO.
Summary: sitting outside and noticed a bright fireball large craft directly above me going west very low, Not a sound was made
